# Cloudflare Tunnel token
# 1. Go to https://one.dash.cloudflare.com/ → Zero Trust → Networks → Tunnels
# 2. Create a new tunnel, copy the token shown during setup
# 3. Set the tunnel's Public Hostname to point to: http://ai-token-calculator:80
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in your token:
#      cp .env.example .env

